Interface TemplateSynchronisationSource<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of configuration data
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface TemplateSynchronisationSource<T>
    Defines where branch names come from when synchronising a template definition with a list of template instances.
